                <UserObject label="&lt;span&gt;  fit(X: DataFrame, y: Series) → None&#xa;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    ← no-op, rules are hand tuned, but must be implemented&#xa;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;  predict(features: Dict) → Tuple[int, str]&#xa;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    ← runs _score() and maps to danger_level + action&#xa;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;  save(path: str) → None&#xa;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    ← saves weights and thresholds to json file&#xa;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;  load(path: str) → None&#xa;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    ← loads weights and thresholds from json file&#xa;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;  feature_importance() → Dict[str, float]&#xa;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    ← returns weights dict as importance proxy&#xa;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;  _score(features: Dict) → float&#xa;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    ← private, weighted sum across feature vector&#xa;&lt;/span&gt;" link="&lt;div class=&quot;relative group/copy bg-bg-000/50 border-0.5 border-border-400 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-accent-100&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot; aria-label=&quot;python code&quot; role=&quot;group&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;overflow-x-auto&quot;&gt;&lt;pre style=&quot;color: rgb(234, 236, 240); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono);&quot; class=&quot;code-block__code !my-0 !rounded-lg !text-sm !leading-relaxed p-3.5&quot;&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;color: rgb(234, 236, 240); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono); white-space: pre;&quot; class=&quot;language-python&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(211, 215, 222);&quot; class=&quot;token token decorator annotation&quot;&gt;@abstractmethod&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#xa;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(204, 123, 244);&quot; class=&quot;token token&quot;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(112, 184, 25