                <UserObject label="&lt;span&gt;  fit(X: DataFrame, y: Series) → None&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    ← trains LSTM/1D-CNN on sequence data from chain&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    ← reshapes X into (samples, sequence_len, features)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;  predict(features: Dict) → Tuple[int, str]&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    ← reshapes input, runs forward pass, returns (danger_level, action)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;  save(path: str) → None&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    ← saves model weights to .pt or .h5 file&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;  load(path: str) → None&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    ← loads model weights from file back into _model&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;  feature_importance() → Dict[str, float]&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    ← approximated via permutation importance&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    ← return _importance_cached&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;" link="&lt;div class=&quot;relative group/copy bg-bg-000/50 border-0.5 border-border-400 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-accent-100&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot; aria-label=&quot;python code&quot; role=&quot;group&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;overflow-x-auto&quot;&gt;&lt;pre style=&quot;color: rgb(234, 236, 240); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono);&quot; class=&quot;code-block__code !my-0 !rounded-lg !text-sm !leading-relaxed p-3.5&quot;&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;color: rgb(234, 236, 240); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono); white-space: pre;&quot; class=&quot;language-python&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(211, 215, 222);&quot; class=&quot;token token decorator annotation&quot;&gt;@abstractmethod&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#xa;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(204, 123, 244);&quot; class=&quot;token token&quot;&gt;def&lt;/sp